des: Work out with Alexa throughout the week. Once you open the skill, just ask Alexa to start the workout.This is design to help you to get closer to your workout goal by motivating you with quotes and other key phrases. You can also ask Alexa for your progress to see how well you are doing. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
